{"type":"message","id":"be66520c","parentId":"d2ec79af","timestamp":"2026-06-09T02:16:47.387Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"结果：\n\n1. **TAPD 周以天** ✅ - 有效，cookie 续期到 2026-06-16\n2. **DevOps** ❌ - Cookie 过期，被重定向到 Keycloak 登录页，需要重新登录\n3. **GitLab** ✅ - 有效，CSRF token 正常刷新\n\nDevOps Cookie 过期了，我需要通知主人。然后用 headless:false 模式打开 DevOps 登录页，让主人扫码登录。\n\n不过主人说的是\"检查cookie活性\"，那我就报告结果。如果 DevOps 需要重登，我可以提供帮助。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"结果出来了：\n\n---\n\n**📊 Cookie 活性检查报告**\n\n| 系统 | 状态 | 详情 |\n|------|------|------|\n| ✅ **TAPD（周以天）** | **有效** | tapdsession 续期至 6月16日 |\n| ✅ **GitLab** | **有效** | session + CSRF token 正常 |\n| ❌ **DevOps** | **已过期** | 被重定向到 Keycloak 登录页 |\n\nDevOps 的 cookie 过期了（重定向到了 Keycloak 密码登录页）。需要我打开 headed 浏览器让你重新登录吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":783,"output":265,"cacheRead":21248,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22296,"cost":{"input":0.00010962000000000001,"output":0.0000742,"cacheRead":0.000594944,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000778764}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780971404381,"responseId":"cd5d1bc5-4ed1-4fbe-a93f-0f8c0be50962"}}
