{"type":"message","id":"7806c9e2","parentId":"a65152e8","timestamp":"2026-06-09T02:19:33.521Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人说\"DevOps cookie加入保活\"，意思是 DevOps 的 cookie 也要像 TAPD 和 GitLab 一样加入日常保活（HEARTBEAT）。\n\n我看一下现有的保活机制。HEARTBEAT.md 里已经有 TAPD（双账号）、DevOps、GitLab 的保活配置了。\n\n等等，HEARTBEAT.md 里已经有 DevOps 保活了：\n\n```markdown\n### DevOps 保活\n\n- 状态文件：`memory/devops-keepalive-state.json`\n- 脚本：`node scripts/devops_keepalive.mjs`\n- 退出码：\n  - `0` → ✅ 成功续期\n  - `1` → ❌ 需要重新登录 DevOps，**主动通知主人**\n  - `2` → ⚠️ 脚本错误，记录到当天 memory 文件\n- Cookie：`workspace/devops_cookies.json`\n```\n\n那为什么 DevOps cookie 还是过期了呢？可能是保活脚本没有正常运行，或者保活 HEARTBEAT 没有成功执行 DevOps 的保活。\n\n让我看看 HEARTBEAT.md 里关于 DevOps 的执行逻辑。HEARTBEAT.md 只是列出了配置，实际的保活逻辑是在 heartbeat 的心跳处理逻辑里。\n\n让我检查一下保活状态文件，看看 DevOps 上次保活时间。\n\n另外，我再看一下 devops_keepalive.mjs 脚本，看看它怎么保存 cookie 的。\n\n不过主人说\"DevOps cookie加入保活\"，可能是指：\n1. DevOps cookie 之前有过保活配置但没生效，让我修复\n2. 或者他之前没有配置 DevOps 保活，现在让我加上\n\n从 MEMORY.md 来看，DevOps 保活是 2026-05-19 加上的，HEARTBEAT.md 里也有配置。但刚才检查 cookie 还是过期了，说明保活可能没跑起来，或者 cookie 保存有问题。\n\n让我先看看 devops_keepalive.mjs 脚本和保活状态文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，我看一下现有的 DevOps 保活配置为什么没生效。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_otX2LPgHkQCRXu7IreIH7030","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"type C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\devops-keepalive-state.json 2>nul || echo \"文件不存在\"","timeout":5}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_cdrAyjw3VJfitIoJTZfI4781","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\devops_keepalive.mjs"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_02_2U3LgAe05EvHgtpcgRoE9142","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":3959,"output":646,"cacheRead":19584,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24189,"cost":{"input":0.00055426,"output":0.00018088000000000002,"cacheRead":0.000548352,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001283492}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780971566971,"responseId":"7e621242-b5c1-4019-903d-40dc533cc565"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c466ce1c","parentId":"7806c9e2","timestamp":"2026-06-09T02:19:33.931Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_otX2LPgHkQCRXu7IreIH7030","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"所在位置 行:1 字符: 87\r\n+ ... penclaw\\workspace\\memory\\devops-keepalive-state.json 2>nul || echo \"文 ...\r\n+                                                                ~~\r\n标记“||”不是此版本中的有效语句分隔符。\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : ParserError: (:) [], ParentContainsErrorRecordException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : InvalidEndOfLine\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":372,"aggregated":"所在位置 行:1 字符: 87\r\n+ ... penclaw\\workspace\\memory\\devops-keepalive-state.json 2>nul || echo \"文 ...\r\n+                                                                ~~\r\n标记“||”不是此版本中的有效语句分隔符。\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : ParserError: (:) [], ParentContainsErrorRecordException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : InvalidEndOfLine\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780971573931}}
{"type":"message","id":"84f0d29c","parentId":"c466ce1c","timestamp":"2026-06-09T02:19:33.932Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_01_cdrAyjw3VJfitIoJTZfI4781","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// DevOps Cookie Keepalive Script\n// Loads cookies, visits the DevOps pipelines page to refresh server-side session,\n// then saves the new cookies back to devops_cookies.json.\n// Run periodically (every 1-2 days) to keep login alive.\n//\n// Exit codes:\n//   0 = success (cookies refreshed)\n//   1 = cookie invalid / login expired (need re-login)\n//   2 = script error (network, etc.)\n\nimport { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __filename = fileURLToPath(import.meta.url);\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(__filename);\nconst WORKSPACE_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'devops_cookies.json');\nconst STATE_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'memory', 'devops-keepalive-state.json');\n\nfunction log(msg) {\n  console.log(`[${new Date().toISOString()}] ${msg}`);\n}\n\nfunction writeState(state) {\n  try {\n    fs.mkdirSync(path.dirname(STATE_FILE), { recursive: true });\n    fs.writeFileSync(STATE_FILE, JSON.stringify(state, null, 2));\n  } catch (e) {\n    console.error('Failed to write state:', e.message);\n  }\n}\n\nasync function main() {\n  if (!fs.existsSync(COOKIES_FILE)) {\n    log(`ERROR: cookies file not found: ${COOKIES_FILE}`);\n    writeState({ ok: false, error: 'cookies_missing', at: new Date().toISOString() });\n    process.exit(1);\n  }\n\n  const oldCookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, 'utf8'));\n  log(`Loaded ${oldCookies.length} cookies`);\n\n  const browser = await chromium.launch({\n    headless: true,\n    args: ['--no-sandbox', '--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled'],\n  });\n  const ctx = await browser.newContext({\n    locale: 'zh-CN',\n    viewport: { width: 1920, height: 1080 },\n    ignoreHTTPSErrors: true,\n  });\n  await ctx.addCookies(oldCookies);\n  const page = await ctx.newPage();\n\n  try {\n    log('Visiting DevOps pipelines page...');\n    const resp = await page.goto('https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines', {\n      waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded',\n      timeout: 30000,\n    });\n    await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n\n    const url = page.url();\n    const title = await page.title();\n    const status = resp?.status();\n    const bodyText = await page.evaluate(() => document.body.innerText.substring(0, 500));\n    log(`HTTP ${status} | url=${url} | title=${title}`);\n    log(`Body preview: ${bodyText.substring(0, 200)}`);\n\n    // Check if we got redirected to login\n    if (url.includes('login') || title.includes('登录') || title.includes('LOGIN') || bodyText.includes('登录')) {\n      log('❌ Session EXPIRED - need re-login');\n      writeState({\n        ok: false,\n        error: 'session_expired',\n        at: new Date().toISOString(),\n        finalUrl: url,\n        title,\n      });\n      await browser.close();\n      process.exit(1);\n    }\n\n    // Also visit the pipeline detail page to deepen the session\n    await page.goto('https://devops.devcloud.ztgame.com/projects/yyzy/pipelines/p-f78c977835c84b71a6d58b4746cd1c4a', {\n      waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded',\n      timeout: 30000,\n    }).catch(() => {});\n    await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n\n    // Save refreshed cookies\n    const newCookies = await ctx.cookies();\n    fs.writeFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, JSON.stringify(newCookies, null, 2));\n\n    log(`✅ Refreshed ${newCookies.length} cookies`);\n    writeState({\n      ok: true,\n      at: new Date().toISOString(),\n      cookieCount: newCookies.length,\n      title,\n    });\n\n    await browser.close();\n    process.exit(0);\n  } catch (e) {\n    log(`ERROR: ${e.message}`);\n    writeState({ ok: false, error: e.message, at: new Date().toISOString() });\n    try { await browser.close(); } catch {}\n    process.exit(2);\n  }\n}\n\nmain();\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780971573931}}
{"type":"message","id":"dc90aeae","parentId":"84f0d29c","timestamp":"2026-06-09T02:19:33.932Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_02_2U3LgAe05EvHgtpcgRoE9142","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Heartbeat Tasks\n\n## 登录保活（每天一次）\n\n每天检查保活状态文件，如果距离上次执行 > 20 小时则自动执行。\n\n### TAPD 保活（双账号）\n\n- 周以天（提单用）：`node scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs`（默认）\n  - Cookie：`tapd_cookies_zhouyitian.json`\n  - 状态：`memory/tapd-keepalive-state-zhouyitian.json`\n- 叶枝君：`node scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs yezhijun`\n  - Cookie：`tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json`\n  - 状态：`memory/tapd-keepalive-state-yezhijun.json`\n- 两个账号每天都要跑一次保活\n- 退出码：\n  - `0` → ✅ 成功续期\n  - `1` → ❌ 需要重新扫码登录 TAPD，**主动通知主人**\n  - `2` → ⚠️ 脚本错误，记录到当天 memory 文件\n- Cookie：`workspace/tapd_cookies.json`\n\n### DevOps 保活\n\n- 状态文件：`memory/devops-keepalive-state.json`\n- 脚本：`node scripts/devops_keepalive.mjs`\n- 退出码：\n  - `0` → ✅ 成功续期\n  - `1` → ❌ 需要重新登录 DevOps，**主动通知主人**\n  - `2` → ⚠️ 脚本错误，记录到当天 memory 文件\n- Cookie：`workspace/devops_cookies.json`\n\n### GitLab 保活\n\n- 状态文件：`memory/gitlab-keepalive-state.json`\n- 脚本：`node scripts/gitlab_keepalive.mjs`\n- 退出码：\n  - `0` → ✅ 成功续期（Cookie + CSRF Token）\n  - `1` → ❌ 需要重新登录 GitLab（SSO），**主动通知主人**\n  - `2` → ⚠️ 脚本错误，记录到当天 memory 文件\n- Cookie：`workspace/gitlab_cookies.json`\n- CSRF：`workspace/gitlab_csrf.json`\n\n**保活原理：** 访问一次页面，服务器端 session 会自动续期，同时提取新 CSRF Token。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780971573932}}
{"type":"message","id":"07477954","parentId":"dc90aeae","timestamp":"2026-06-09T02:19:39.058Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"HEARTBEAT.md 里已经有 DevOps 保活的配置了。但 DevOps cookie 还是过期了，说明：\n1. 保活脚本虽然在 HEARTBEAT.md 里配置了，但 HEARTBEAT 心跳可能没有实际执行 DevOps 的保活\n2. 或者上次保活后 cookie 又过期了（DevOps 的 session 有效期可能很短）\n\n让我看看 devops-keepalive-state.json 是否存在以及上次保活时间。\n\n其实 HEARTBEAT.md 只是文档，实际的 HEARTBEAT 执行逻辑是内置在主 session 中的。主 session 收到心跳时会根据 HEARTBEAT.md 的内容去执行相应操作。\n\n但是等等，HEARTBEAT.md 只是被作为 context 加载给 agent 的参考文档，实际是否执行保活取决于 agent 在心跳时读没读它。\n\n不过主人在让我\"加入保活\"，说明他确认目前 DevOps cookie 没有成功保活。我应该看看问题出在哪。\n\n刚才检查 DevOps cookie 时，保活脚本说 session expired（code 1），因为 cookie 过期了。但 cookie 为什么会过期？可能是因为：\n1. 保活脚本确实没被定期执行\n2. 或者 cookie 有效期很短\n\n让我查看一下状态文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_eX2Usui42jsz54OPpGbG5139","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"powershell -Command \"Get-Content 'C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\devops-keepalive-state.json' -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue; if (-not $?) { echo '文件不存在' }\"","timeout":5}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_tZ6xEQ1tG5WBXodBORsi9993","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"powershell -Command \"Get-ChildItem 'C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\devops_cookies.json' | Select-Object LastWriteTime\"","timeout":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1794,"output":469,"cacheRead":24064,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26327,"cost":{"input":0.00025116,"output":0.00013132,"cacheRead":0.000673792,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001056272}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780971573933,"responseId":"220d1ca7-11a1-4b50-b0ff-ad1442361c1b"}}
