{"type":"message","id":"c4f303c6","parentId":"19c5ec7c","timestamp":"2026-06-09T03:20:04.824Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"日志文件的最后修改时间是 2026/6/4 11:56，也就是 6月4日。这说明 sub-agent 虽然执行了 bat，但 Unity 并没有写入新的日志到 `BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log` 文件。也就是说：\n\n1. bat 文件可能执行了（Unity 启动了）\n2. 但 Unity 流水线并没有写出新的日志\n3. 或者 Unity 流水线执行但输出到了不同的日志文件\n\n等等，让我重新看看 bat 文件的内容和日志文件名。\n\n`BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log` 是 6月4日的，也就是 5 天前的。说明 sub-agent 执行的 Unity 流水线可能往不同的文件写了日志，或者确实没执行成功。\n\n主人说他自己手动执行了，说明流水线本身是有问题的——可能是 sub-agent 执行的 bat 没有正确触发流水线。\n\n让我看看 bat 文件的内容。\n\n问题可能出在：\n1. bat 实际调用了 Unity，但参数不对（比如 `-executeMethod` 的类名/方法名写错了？）\n2. 或者 Unity 打开后因为某些原因（License、项目加载失败）没有执行到流水线\n3. 或者 Unity 虽然执行了但输出到了不同的日志文件\n\n让我看看 bat 文件的内容。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"日志更新时间是 **6月4日**——说明 sub-agent 执行的 Unity 确实没写入新日志，热更流水线没有实际运行。我来查一下 bat 文件的内容，看是不是参数问题。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_5TUcgm1jSlGIFxzpEVIU6186","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1237,"output":380,"cacheRead":32512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34129,"cost":{"input":0.00017318000000000002,"output":0.00010640000000000001,"cacheRead":0.000910336,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001189916}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780975200313,"responseId":"f2a95b6b-8d51-4066-851b-9f03e22a7de9"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f1cb0176","parentId":"c4f303c6","timestamp":"2026-06-09T03:20:04.845Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_5TUcgm1jSlGIFxzpEVIU6186","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"@echo off\r\nchcp 65001 >nul 2>&1\r\nsetlocal\r\n\r\n:: 与 PlatformSwitcher.bat 一致：按本机安装修改 Unity 路径\r\nset \"UNITY_PATH=C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\2020.3.49f1\\Editor\\Unity.exe\"\r\n\r\ncd /d \"%~dp0\" || exit /b 1\r\nset \"PROJECT_PATH=%CD%\"\r\nset \"LOG_FILE=%PROJECT_PATH%\\BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log\"\r\n\r\nif not exist \"%UNITY_PATH%\" (\r\n    echo [ERROR] 未找到 Unity.exe，请编辑本 bat 中的 UNITY_PATH。\r\n    exit /b 1\r\n)\r\n\r\necho [INFO] projectPath=%PROJECT_PATH%\r\necho [INFO] 执行无参 RunHotUpdatePipeline：流水线「热更」的全部有效步骤\r\necho [INFO] log=%LOG_FILE%\r\n\r\n\"%UNITY_PATH%\" -batchmode -quit -nographics -buildTarget Android -projectPath \"%PROJECT_PATH%\" -executeMethod YYZY.BuildPipeline.BuildPipeline.RunHotUpdatePipeline -logFile \"%LOG_FILE%\"\r\n\r\necho [INFO] Unity 退出码: %ERRORLEVEL%\r\nexit /b %ERRORLEVEL%\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780975204845}}
{"type":"message","id":"80d9b9a1","parentId":"f1cb0176","timestamp":"2026-06-09T03:20:09.042Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bat 文件看起来参数都没问题，`-executeMethod YYZY.BuildPipeline.BuildPipeline.RunHotUpdatePipeline` 和之前配置的一致。\n\n日志文件 `BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log` 的修改时间是 6月4日，说明 sub-agent 的 Unity 被调用了但没有写入新日志。这可能有几种情况：\n\n1. Unity 进程没有正确执行（比如 License 问题、项目加载失败等）\n2. Unity 启动后立即退出了，没有走到流水线\n3. Unity 把日志写到了其他地方\n\n让我检查一下是否有其他日志文件，或者看看 Unity 是否在运行时产生了错误。\n\n等等，主人说他\"自己手动执行了\"，说明他手动跑了同样的 bat 或者直接在 Unity Editor 里跑了流水线，并且成功了。问题可能是 sub-agent 在运行 bat 时 Unity 被卡住了或者没有正常执行。\n\n让我搜一下是否有其他的日志输出。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_To1wJI4zCAKADFz7jLd77918","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"powershell -Command \"Get-ChildItem 'E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\BuildPipeline_*.log' | Select-Object Name, Length, LastWriteTime | Format-Table -AutoSize\"","timeout":5}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_RuykV6JzUMSkVrKb7aE66090","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"powershell -Command \"Get-ChildItem 'C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\AppData\\Local\\Unity\\Editor\\' -Filter 'Editor.log' -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object FullName, LastWriteTime, Length\"","timeout":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":394,"output":401,"cacheRead":34048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34843,"cost":{"input":0.00005516,"output":0.00011228,"cacheRead":0.000953344,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0011207839999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780975204846,"responseId":"9d1dd43f-c757-45ec-9bab-fe868f516751"}}
