{"type":"message","id":"34234183","parentId":"26f8a4b5","timestamp":"2026-06-09T03:20:24.584Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Can't see the sub-agent's history. But the key evidence is clear:\n\n1. `BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log` - last modified June 4\n2. `Editor.log` - 0 bytes, last modified 10:56\n\nSo when the sub-agent ran the bat file:\n- Unity DID launch (Editor.log timestamp updated)\n- But it didn't write to `BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log` \n- And `Editor.log` is 0 bytes, which is unusual\n\nThis could mean:\n1. Unity started but crashed before writing anything\n2. Unity ran but the log was written to a different file\n3. The bat ran but Unity couldn't acquire the license\n4. The Unity process was killed/stopped prematurely\n\nThe sub-agent reported \"Unity 退出正常\" and \"无错误\" - it was checking a log file that hadn't been updated, so of course it found no errors. This is a bug in the sub-agent flow.\n\nThe issue is that the sub-agent executed the bat but Unity might have:\n- Had a license issue (common with batchmode)\n- Crashed during project loading\n- The `-executeMethod` class might not have compiled/loaded properly\n\nSince `Editor.log` is 0 bytes, it seems like Unity started but exited immediately without writing anything substantial. This could be a license issue or a crash during startup.\n\nI should report my findings to the主人 and let him know what happened. The bat file itself looks correct, but the Unity execution in sub-agent silently failed (no log output).","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到原因了。查了一下日志：\n\n- `BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log` — 最后更新是 **6月4日**，sub-agent 跑完后**没有新写入**\n- `Editor.log` — 0 字节，最后修改 10:56，说明 Unity 启动了但**什么日志都没写出来就退出了**\n\n**问题根因：** sub-agent 执行 bat 后，Unity 进程启动但**没有成功执行流水线**（可能是许可证校验失败 / 项目加载异常 / 方法未找到等），但 exit code 返回了 0，sub-agent 误以为成功，检查的还是旧日志。\n\nbat 的参数字符串本身没问题（`-executeMethod YYZY.BuildPipeline.BuildPipeline.RunHotUpdatePipeline`），大概率是 Unity batch mode 启动时遇到了异常退出的情况，但没有写日志。\n\n最好的改进方案：\n1. sub-agent 执行 bat 后，检查**日志文件的时间戳是否有更新**来判断流水线是否真的跑了\n2. 再检查 `Editor.log` 是否有错误信息\n\n我一起看一下 Editor.log 有没有记录错误？"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_5g54fWRpK6A0IGL7whmi1525","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"powershell -Command \"Get-Content 'C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\AppData\\Local\\Unity\\Editor\\Editor.log' -Tail 200\"","timeout":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":82,"output":655,"cacheRead":35584,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36321,"cost":{"input":0.00001148,"output":0.0001834,"cacheRead":0.000996352,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001191232}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780975217411,"responseId":"6db327c3-17ed-424a-a0be-49acce1e14cc"}}
