{"type":"message","id":"5437ac87","parentId":"d57eb8fe","timestamp":"2026-06-09T03:21:01.163Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The spawn UNKNOWN error - I need to run this as a bat file or use a simpler command. Let me write the update to TOOLS.md using the write tool instead.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_yeGypjH15GUg0x1p14oF9023","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\temp_fix.js","content":"const fs = require('fs');\nlet content = fs.readFileSync('C:\\\\Users\\\\yyzypublic\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\TOOLS.md', 'utf8');\n\nconst oldSection = `**编译失败检测逻辑：**\n- ⚠️ **Unity 退出码为 0 不代表流水线完全成功！** 流水线内部步骤可能失败（如 git pull），但 Unity 仍以 0 退出\n- 必须额外扫描日志文件，检测以下致命错误：\n  - \\`error CS\\\\d+:\\` — C# 编译报错（硬错误）\n  - \\`git更新失败\\` — 流水线内 git pull 失败\n  - \\`Build completed with.*errors\\` — Unity 构建统计有 errors\n- 检查命令：\\`powershell -Command \"Select-String -Path 'E:\\\\Solo\\\\nightoffullmoon\\\\client\\\\cardv\\\\BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log' -Pattern 'error CS\\\\d+:|git更新失败|Build completed with'\"\\`\n- 匹配到关键字 → **视为失败**，发失败通知（hotupdate-fail）\n- 无匹配 + Unity 退出码 0 → **视为成功**，发成功通知（hotupdate-ok）`;\n\nconst newSection = `**编译结果检测逻辑（两步校验）：**\n\n**第一步：检查日志是否已更新（防假阳性）**\n- ⚠️ **Unity 退出码为 0 不代表流水线真正跑了！** 可能 Unity 进程异常退出但 exit code 还是 0\n- 在运行 bat 前先记录 \\`BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log\\` 的 LastWriteTime\n- bat 执行完后，重新检查该文件的 LastWriteTime\n- **如果时间没有变化 → 流水线没有实际执行，视为失败**\n- 同时检查 \\`Editor.log\\`（\\`%USERPROFILE%/AppData/Local/Unity/Editor/Editor.log\\`）是否有本次运行的线索\n\n**第二步：扫描日志内容（防部分失败）**\n如果日志时间戳已更新，扫描检测以下致命错误：\n  - \\`error CS\\\\d+:\\` — C# 编译报错（硬错误）\n  - \\`git更新失败\\` — 流水线内 git pull 失败\n  - \\`Build completed with.*errors\\` — Unity 构建统计有 errors\n- 检查命令：\\`powershell -Command \"Select-String -Path 'E:\\\\Solo\\\\nightoffullmoon\\\\client\\\\cardv\\\\BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log' -Pattern 'error CS\\\\d+:|git更新失败|Build completed with'\"\\`\n- 匹配到关键字 → *