{"type":"message","id":"8cdb1fd8","parentId":"bd172501","timestamp":"2026-06-09T03:21:08.072Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me summarize the findings and the fix for the主人.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了，root cause 找到了。总结一下：\n\n---\n\n**🔍 根因分析：**\n\nsub-agent 跑 bat 后 Unity batch 进程**没有实际执行流水线**（可能 License 校验/项目加载异常/进程启动有问题），但：\n- Unity exit code = 0（误以为成功）\n- sub-agent 去扫 `BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log`，发现**没有错误关键字** → 报告成功\n- 但实际上日志文件**根本没更新**（还是 6月4日的），完全是假阳性\n\n**🛠️ 已修复（TOOLS.md 热更流程）：**\n\n现在加了**两步校验**，不再只看日志内容：\n\n1. **第一步 — 时间戳校验**：跑 bat 前记录日志的 LastWriteTime，跑完后对比，**时间没变直接判失败**\n2. **第二步 — 内容扫描**：时间戳变了才去扫错误关键字\n\n同时会检查 `Editor.log` 是否有线索。这样以后不会再出现\"报告成功但实际没跑\"的情况了。抱歉刚才的假报告 🙇"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":119,"output":246,"cacheRead":46848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47213,"cost":{"input":0.00001666,"output":0.00006888,"cacheRead":0.0013117439999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001397284}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780975264690,"responseId":"ef3d6a44-e757-4e66-9d22-e5c2ad2c3671"}}
