{"type":"message","id":"a024776f","parentId":"953b7319","timestamp":"2026-06-09T03:44:48.625Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The log file is still from June 4. I'll record this timestamp and pass it to the sub-agent so it can check if the file gets updated after running the bat.\n\nNow let me spawn the sub-agent to:\n1. Update submodules\n2. Run the bat\n3. Check if log timestamp changed\n4. Scan for errors\n5. Notify","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_4OrA9CmtJqgWXDoOkJNt7201","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"label":"hotupdate-v2","mode":"run","context":"isolated","task":"执行客户端热更流水线（更新测试包）\n\n**前置步骤已完成（在主 session 执行过）：**\n1. ✅ 检查 Unity 进程 — 已关掉 Unity Editor (PID 42760)\n2. ✅ git pull 主仓库 `E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon` — Fast-forward, 72 files updated\n3. ✅ 已记录日志时间戳：`2026-06-04T11:56:09`\n\n## 你需要执行的步骤\n\n### 第一步：更新子模块\n进入 `E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon` 目录，检查子模块：\n1. `git submodule status` 查看状态\n2. 对每个子模块检查 detached HEAD：`git symbolic-ref -q HEAD`\n3. 如果 detached，从 `.gitmodules` 确定正确分支，`git checkout <branch>` + `git pull`\n4. 确保所有子模块指向正确分支的最新提交\n\n### 第二步：运行热更流水线\n直接执行 bat：\n```\nE:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat\n```\n⚠️ 直接输入 bat 路径，不要包 cmd /c 或 powershell -Command\n⚠️ 不要用内联多行 PowerShell 脚本\n\n### 第三步：检查编译结果（两步校验）\n\n**① 检查日志时间戳是否更新**\n用 PowerShell 检查：\n```powershell\n(Get-Item 'E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log').LastWriteTime.ToString('o')\n```\n比较是否不等于 `2026-06-04T11:56:09`。\n- 时间没变 → **流水线没执行**，视为失败\n- 同时检查 `Editor.log`（`C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\AppData\\Local\\Unity\\Editor\\Editor.log`）看是否有此运行的线索\n\n**② 扫描日志错误关键字**\n如果时间戳已更新，扫描：\n```powershell\nSelect-String -Path 'E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log' -Pattern 'error CS\\d+:|git更新失败|Build completed with'\n```\n- 匹配到 → 视为失败\n- 无匹配 → 视为成功\n\n### 第四步：通知\n- ✅ **成功** → 发群消息：`node C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\feishu_send_group.mjs oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77 hotupdate-ok`\n- ❌ **失败** → 只私聊通知主人（sessions_send），**不在群里发**\n\n### 重要提醒\n- 每个步骤状态变化都要通过飞书消息及时反馈给主人\n- ⚠️ Unity 退出码 0 不代表流水线真正跑了！必须检查日志时间戳\n- 如果时间戳没变但 Editor.log 有内容，说明 Unity 启动但没走流水线，也是失败"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":151,"output":840,"cacheRead":54656,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55647,"cost":{"input":0.00002114,"output":0.00023520000000000002,"cacheRead":0.001530368,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017867080000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780976682004,"responseId":"fe3cfac1-d5a9-4ef0-907f-8ac5bb045865"}}
